text:
Was scared with 50% kidney function, 2 artificial heart valves & other hassles after sepsis.
Phoned Doc & he said "You're group 6, mid May, maybe. Bye!".
Two hours pass, an SMS arrives.
Invitation for vaccination @ 17:10 today!
Woohoo!
